dct_description_sm: This flat map, prepared in November of 2018 by Data You Can Use, presentd population change for the City of Milwaukee from 2010-2016. The map utilizes 2010 census data, the 2012-2016 American Community Survey 5-year Estimate, and 2010 Census tracts. For more information, please visit
